---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-24 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 pattern-bg z-0"></div>
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter relative z-10 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<span class="inline-block py-1 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed font-label-caps text-label-caps mb-6">BIIDZNILLAH, MEMBENTUK GENERASI RABBANI</span>
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg text-primary mb-6">Tarbiyah Sunnah Lab School</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 leading-relaxed">Sekolah Islam yang mendampingi anak tumbuh dengan iman, adab, ilmu, dan karakter rabbani sejak usia dini hingga sekolah dasar.</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-primary-container transition-all">Daftar SPMB</button>
<a href="http://wa.me/6285173396002" class="bg-secondary text-on-secondary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-on-secondary-container transition-all inline-block">Konsultasi School Center</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-8 flex gap-6 text-primary">
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold hover:underline" href="#preschool"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="child_care">child_care</span> Program Preschool</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold hover:underline" href="#elementary"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="school">school</span> Program Elementary</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative group">
<div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border-2 border-secondary rounded-lg -z-10 group-hover:top-0 group-hover:right-0 transition-all duration-500"></div>
<div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl h-[500px]">
<img alt="School Exterior" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A grand architectural view of a modern Islamic school building with natural wood accents and large windows. The lighting is golden hour sun, casting soft warm shadows across the clean courtyard. The atmosphere is serene, academic, and professional, reflecting the organic academic design system with sage green and terracotta tones in the landscaping." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDviLjcDWT3n-UTFGVzp8OS36GpzCZU7_A1GvjjYf_T2CFXGdEuvycsJzEULuscqLH9ZaGgAbkKlg7J0O9V3PUe_7tNmdSthX1EKkrlsaxUi_0xZmGEzUfUfqNgfVqm58jKxQv94F7TjDnEqrITOHYZoyjU75QT2XTkcUKBu0kUSeQRGzHw6syn0Iv7zAU8AUehbNxw5aL_wM1RqSPMLBBJZ1VjjYGe20DDmBQBSf09oImQMhmInVdoEv9Jguvw-eajFtd6sI4JgdoVRA">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Jenjang Pendidikan (Two Large Cards) -->
<section class="py-section-padding-desktop bg-surface-container-low wood-texture">
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Jenjang Pendidikan</h2>
<p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-on-surface-variant">Kurikulum yang dirancang khusus untuk memenuhi kebutuhan tumbuh kembang anak sesuai fitrahnya.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
<!-- Preschool Card -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col hover:shadow-md transition-shadow" id="preschool">
<div class="h-64">
<img alt="Preschool Area" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A warm and inviting preschool classroom featuring natural wooden furniture and soft earth-tone decorations. Large windows allow natural light to fill the space where sensory play materials like sand and wooden blocks are arranged neatly. The environment feels calm and nurturing, specifically designed for early childhood development in an Islamic context." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCF0Ysoc5sdQ417ET7R_ZyE1g8CPtl4ZhhXWgjWngFuBb3xn1XRWUiCagvDqLybm-Novby6xkyDsMV9fEdHxEAw_FmmxcIX-nkG_LxQBKXlnvWX4SDuaEALnShbUwZeKbfZOaWrUjKo_Ylr2ZD6E8ukD0LUU7hHZ8ok40yMI9VWHqk8CKDt1zG21dOg6BnYClOc1V2vGXdT5LRIjuMJPFgqf5N9RbOha_wMUG5qDfJdwMgW94QR39DJ0ZWn7-zlZzbt2PsC2Mb2WoRXPQ">
</div>
<div class="p-10">
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-secondary mb-4">Preschool (PAUD)</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6">Masa keemasan anak adalah waktu terbaik menanamkan kecintaan pada Allah. Dengan pendekatan ramah anak dan bermain sambil belajar, kami mendampingi ananda mengenal adab dan kemandirian sejak dini dalam suasana yang hangat dan ceria.</p>
<ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-on-surface">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span> Kurikulum Khas</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span> Stimulasi Motorik &amp; Sensorik</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span> Tahfidz Surat Pendek</li>
</ul>
<button class="w-full border-2 border-secondary text-secondary py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-secondary hover:text-white transition-all">Detail Program Preschool</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Elementary Card -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col hover:shadow-md transition-shadow" id="elementary">
<div class="h-64">
<img alt="Elementary Library" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A clean and disciplined elementary school library with rows of organized books including Islamic literature and science texts. The room features high ceilings and minimalist modern furniture in deep olive and warm wood tones. The atmosphere is academic and studious, reflecting a balance of classical scholarship and modern learning tools." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAbkVi3CexN09LsOFBvvyHOv3spIyweck2wkYJUjkkyXVgY8ypXfQApQe5QJnmxfBzY4XEkOqrcC0yMBZb3L2Drw7UemKJWGYoUbkYcQvanu6zHvMGmHO0zdsB7ynKgLH3rRV81nR95QjQqUb15Btu30YIKez0NoarY84DW47CtwIHxDW8WDBDPs11YU7aVVPAY-R_8WRf4LX0eEOq7gJoUyCsSOgmUPYnKzXfqa7HZUjqjKV6NUn2c77vQDWclEYV9QmGi1oZy954kAg">
</div>
<div class="p-10">
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Elementary (SD)</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6">Membangun fondasi akademik yang kokoh dengan integrasi nilai-nilai keislaman yang mendalam. Siswa diajak untuk berpikir kritis, berakhlak mulia, dan memiliki kedisiplinan tinggi dalam menuntut ilmu syar'i maupun umum.</p>
<ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-on-surface">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span> Kurikulum Nasional Terintegrasi</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span> Program Tahfidz Intensif</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span> Penguatan Literasi &amp; Numerasi</li>
</ul>
<button class="w-full border-2 border-primary text-primary py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all">Detail Program Elementary</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Keunggulan (Bento Grid) -->
<section class="py-section-padding-desktop bg-background">
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Kenapa Memilih Kami?</h2>
<p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-on-surface-variant">Keunggulan strategis yang menjadikan sekolah kami mitra terbaik orang tua dalam mendidik generasi.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<!-- Card 1 -->
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container rounded-lg border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-6" data-icon="mosque">mosque</span>
<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Berbasis Nilai Islam</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Pendidikan yang berlandaskan Al-Qur'an dan As-Sunnah sesuai pemahaman para salafus shalih.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 2 -->
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container rounded-lg border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-6" data-icon="volunteer_activism">volunteer_activism</span>
<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Pendekatan Ramah Anak</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Menciptakan lingkungan yang aman secara psikologis sehingga potensi anak berkembang optimal.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 3 -->
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container rounded-lg border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-6" data-icon="menu_book">menu_book</span>
<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Integrasi Adab</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Adab didahulukan sebelum ilmu, memastikan anak tumbuh dengan karakter yang santun dan mulia.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 4 -->
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container rounded-lg border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-6" data-icon="eco">eco</span>
<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Lingkungan Natural</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Fasilitas yang asri dan dekat dengan alam untuk mendukung kesehatan fisik dan mental anak.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 5 -->
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container rounded-lg border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-6" data-icon="diversity_3">diversity_3</span>
<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Komunikasi Orang Tua</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Sinergi berkelanjutan antara sekolah dan rumah untuk monitoring perkembangan ananda.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 6 -->
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container rounded-lg border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-6" data-icon="devices">devices</span>
<h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Sistem Informasi Sekolah</h4>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Kemudahan akses informasi akademik dan administrasi melalui platform digital terintegrasi.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Program Utama (Asymmetric Layout) -->
<section class="py-section-padding-desktop bg-primary text-on-primary relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full opacity-10">
<svg class="w-full h-full fill-current" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
<path d="M50 0 L100 50 L50 100 L0 50 Z"></path>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter relative z-10">
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
<div class="lg:col-span-5">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-6">Program Unggulan Kurikulum</h2>
<p class="text-body-lg mb-8 opacity-90">Kami menyusun kurikulum yang menyeimbangkan kecakapan spiritual, intelektual, dan sosial budaya.</p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="bg-primary-container p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="auto_stories">auto_stories</span>
</div>
<div>
<h5 class="font-bold text-lg">Al-Qur'an &amp; Hadits</h5>
<p class="opacity-80">Tahfidz, Tahsin, dan pemahaman dasar hadits-hadits harian.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="bg-primary-container p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="psychology">psychology</span>
</div>
<div>
<h5 class="font-bold text-lg">Adab &amp; Akhlak</h5>
<p class="opacity-80">Penerapan nilai-nilai islami dalam interaksi sosial sehari-hari.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="bg-primary-container p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="translate">translate</span>
</div>
<div>
<h5 class="font-bold text-lg">Trilingual Program</h5>
<p class="opacity-80">Pengenalan Bahasa Arab (Diniyyah), Inggris, dan Pelestarian Bahasa Sunda.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="space-y-4">
<img alt="Student Activity" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg aspect-square object-cover" data-alt="A focused close-up of a student's hands carefully holding a traditional Arabic calligraphy pen over textured paper. The lighting is soft and natural, emphasizing the texture of the materials. The setting is a serene, sunlit classroom with olive green accents and wooden furniture, embodying the school's focus on adab and classical Islamic arts." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA8iP7u7gvoJgL7H1-v3p_1deWfjtrjR-KPjyFfgOtMYRc_RCVCQT_RsXizsE1e276zx1bAVhnLjOkkkWv9jieWtCkE4vOWgfrVtHGiC-KjaVzSM9h9D3XSx8-aF28pcJSbmY4llMG7aPDvKgCzIoICtdEmtl_KX0jk1de-NSb3SunMEpCFCxMjQaUfZxXfmbM3wUo3jhiF7t_Lm5wsaezttnRQ3xOCFbEHFj4w3MHkhDbcxNmS0omAHhw5qgt0R0waTyHV8nf3FlI">
