<img alt="Classroom" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg aspect-[3/4] object-cover" data-alt="An empty, well-organized elementary classroom at Tarbiyah Sunnah Lab School. The desks are arranged for collaboration, made from light-colored wood. Large windows look out onto greenery, filling the room with diffused daylight. The walls are a soft warm white, decorated with neat, minimalist educational charts that maintain a calm academic environment." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBjzJX1qlCjzOWhvsS09jv4UTBn18x6bG2ZQFkF_99gI1MO8bcksS54oToq1XITHxxxdZ-IpPB1TPLHwXCxIVQEMVgS0S6LZYiykM9fK-X0Fi8EgZvRS0Flqsu2I5c2snGxZG8NTfSIxs_WbXEmlXKNUItOqxHKT1TzLOQOuseGdqjzTkrq9Jdb1VpJPqmuRvln7veZFnfSL6MCGegRTE5iBEy7ACy5g_M-ZfvzD9Jge23FmeHTB76QM5Osr0EpNUzcfI3gwzqkdFvx6Q">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Latest Articles (Blog) -->
<section class="py-section-padding-desktop bg-background">
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-12 gap-6">
<div>
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Artikel Terbaru</h2>
